<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>I LOVE YOU</title>

<style>

body{
font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
margin:0;
height:100vh;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
background: linear-gradient(135deg,#FEFAE0,#FAEDCD);
overflow:hidden;
text-align:center;
}

.container{
background:white;
padding:40px;
border-radius:20px;
box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
max-width:500px;
}

button{
padding:12px 25px;
margin:10px;
border:none;
border-radius:12px;
font-size:16px;
cursor:pointer;
background:#D3FAC7;
transition:0.2s;
}

button:hover{
background:#B7E4C7;
}

#loveMeter{
width:100%;
}

.hearts{
position:absolute;
font-size:30px;
animation: float 15s linear infinite;
}

@keyframes float{
0%{transform:translateY(100vh)}
100%{transform:translateY(-10vh)}
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container" id="main">

<h1 id="question">Do you like me?</h1>

<button onclick="yes1()">Yes</button>
<button id="noBtn" onclick="no1()">No</button>

</div>


<audio id="music" autoplay loop>
<source src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/audio/2022/03/15/audio_9b59f54d30.mp3">
</audio>

<script>

let stage=1

const main=document.getElementById("main")
const question=document.getElementById("question")

const noBtn=document.getElementById("noBtn")

noBtn.addEventListener("mouseover",()=>{
noBtn.style.position="absolute"
noBtn.style.left=Math.random()*80+"%"
noBtn.style.top=Math.random()*80+"%"
})

function yes1(){

stage=2

main.innerHTML=`

<h1>How much do you love me?</h1>

<input type="range" min="0" max="5000" value="100" id="loveMeter">

<p id="percent">100%</p>

<button onclick="next()">Next ❤️</button>

`

const slider=document.getElementById("loveMeter")
const percent=document.getElementById("percent")

slider.oninput=()=>{
percent.innerText=slider.value+"%"
}

}

function no1(){
alert("I don't like you, I love you ❤️")
}

function next(){

stage=3

main.innerHTML=`

<h1>You are mine and mine alone and you will never ever ever be shared</h1>

<button onclick="agree()">Agree</button>

<button id="runBtn">Disagree</button>

`

const runBtn=document.getElementById("runBtn")

runBtn.addEventListener("mouseover",()=>{
runBtn.style.position="absolute"
runBtn.style.left=Math.random()*80+"%"
runBtn.style.top=Math.random()*80+"%"
})

}

function agree(){

main.innerHTML=`

<h1>You are crazyyyyyy ❤️</h1>

<p>
Hey kouki i know what we’re going through isn’t easy and that this is a rough time but i wanted to tell you how proud i am of youu. You are actually the strongest person i ever met. And you are able to go through things that no one would ever be able to handle.

You are so strong and your faith is even stronger, and i am so proud of you.

I want you to know that i am here for you through everything and that i will never ever leave your side.

Everytime i say I love you more, I don't mean more than you love me.  
I mean I love you more than the bad days ahead of us.  
I love you more than any fight we ever have.  
I love you more than any rough time we go through.  
I love you more than distance.  
I love you more than obstacles.  
I love you more than the odds stacked against me.

I love you more than anything.
</p>

`

createHearts()

}

function createHearts(){

for(let i=0;i<30;i++){

let heart=document.createElement("div")

heart.innerHTML="❤️"

heart.className="hearts"

heart.style.left=Math.random()*100+"%"

heart.style.animationDuration=10+Math.random()*10+"s"

document.body.appendChild(heart)

}

}

</script>

</body>
</html>
